findStrings.find:
\-\-\-
\- hosts\: localhost
 connection\: local
 gather_facts\: no

 vars\:
 bpm_auth_user\: "bpmsAdmin"
 bpm_auth_password\: "bpmsuite1\!"

 tasks\:

 \- name\: Ansible Workflow
 uri\:
 url\: http\://localhost\:8080/kie\-server/services/rest/server/containers/ansiblecontainer\-1/processes/com\.redhat\.demos\.ansibleworkflow\.AnsibleWorkFlow/instances
 method\: POST
 user\: "\{\{ bpm_auth_user \}\}"
 password\: "\{\{ bpm_auth_password \}\}"
 force_basic_auth\: yes
 status_code\: 201
 body_format\: json
 headers\:
 Accept\: application/json
 Content\-Type\: application/json
 X\-KIE\-ContentType\: JSON
\# Requires ansible 1\.8\+
\- name\: 'YUM \- async task'
 yum\:
 name\: docker\-io
 state\: installed
 async\: 1000
 poll\: 0
 register\: yum_sleeper

\- name\: 'YUM \- check on async task'
 async_status\:
 jid\: "\{\{ yum_sleeper\.ansible_job_id \}\}"
 register\: job_result
 until\: job_result\.finished
 retries\: 30
